10190@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Climate@1@1@@oe@20-11-2007
10210@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Finnmark is far north and is thus cold.@1@8@@oe@20-11-2007
10220@unknown@formal@none@1@S@But the Gulf Stream warms the coast, and makes Finnmark relatively mild compared with areas in Siberia and Alaska at the same latitude.@1@23@@oe@20-11-2007
10230@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Usually you will find temperatures between 10 - 20 in the summer.@1@12@@oe@20-11-2007
