15850@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Other animals present are rabbit, red fox, arctic fox, lynx, wolverine and various smaller animals (mouses, weasels, lemmings) as well as different kinds of birds (including everything from small sparrows via seagulls and ravens to eagles).@1@36@@oe@20-11-2007
