16390@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Generally Jotunheimen consists of high mountains and valleys, with a normal difference of 800-1400 metres between the highest peaks and the bottom of the valleys.@1@25@@oe@20-11-2007
16410@unknown@formal@none@1@S@You should take this into account when making your plans.@1@10@@oe@20-11-2007
