24380@unknown@formal@none@1@S@In the winter the sun is gone for four months, of which two months are total dark, without any light even in the middle of the day.@1@27@@oe@20-11-2007
24390@unknown@formal@none@1@S@With stable, cold climate and total dark the conditions are the best for spotting Northern Lights.@1@16@@oe@20-11-2007
